    "text": "This translation key displays a warning title indicating a scheduled change to a subscription, specifically a cancellation of storage. It informs the user of the storage size change (from {{fromSize}} to {{toSize}}) and appears within a dialog or notification in the Portal Settings, likely related to storage upgrades or downgrades. Translators should ensure the sizes and \"Gigabyte\" unit are correctly localized.",
    "is_auto": true,
    "updated_at": "2026-03-20T10:12:44.764Z"
  },
  "usage": [
    {
      "file_path": "/packages/client/src/pages/PortalSettings/categories/payments/SaaS/services/pages/additional-storage/AdditionalStoragePage.tsx",
      "line_number": 153,
      "context": "const isScheduled = !!hasScheduledStorageChange;\n const isDowngrade = isScheduled && !isStorageCancellation();\n \n const warningTitle = isStorageCancellation()\n ? t(\"Services:CancellationScheduled\", {\n fromSize: `${currentStoragePlanSize} ${t(\"Common:Gigabyte\")}`,\n toSize: `${nextStoragePlanSize ?? 0} ${t(\"Common:Gigabyte\")}`,\n })\n : t(\"Services:DowngradeScheduled\", {\n fromSize: `${currentStoragePlanSize} ${t(\"Common:Gigabyte\")}`,",
      "module": "/packages/client"
    }
